sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>(ml-pipeline-api-server)
    participant KFPSDK as KFP SDK (Python)<br/>ml-metadata client
    participant PipelineUI as Pipeline UI / Client
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS + mTLS
    participant MySQL as MySQL / MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>Optional TLS
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP<br/>Optional TLS

    Note over KFP,PostgreSQL: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecution (artifact, events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 Port 8080<br/>Optional mTLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>MySQL: INSERT/UPDATE metadata records<br/>MySQL protocol Port 3306<br/>Username/Password auth
    MySQL-->>MLMD: Query result
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionResponse
    deactivate MLMD

    KFP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts (pipeline output artifacts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 Port 8080
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>MySQL: INSERT artifact records<br/>MySQL protocol Port 3306
    MySQL-->>MLMD: Query result
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutArtifactsResponse
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over KFP,PostgreSQL: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    PipelineUI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 Port 8080<br/>Optional mTLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>MySQL: SELECT lineage graph<br/>(artifacts, executions, events)<br/>MySQL protocol Port 3306
    MySQL-->>MLMD: Graph data
    MLMD-->>PipelineUI: LineageSubgraph response<br/>(nodes + edges)
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over KFP,PostgreSQL: Flow 3: Python SDK Direct Access

    KFPSDK->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 Port 8080<br/>Retry with exponential backoff
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>MySQL: SELECT artifacts<br/>with filter_query + pagination
    MySQL-->>MLMD: Paginated results
    MLMD-->>KFPSDK: GetArtifactsByContextResponse<br/>(with next_page_token)
    deactivate MLMD
